<title>USA: American Brands says gets debt consents.</title>
<headline>American Brands says gets debt consents.</headline>
<dateline>OLD GREENWICH, Conn. 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>American Brands Inc said it sucessfully completed a consent solicitation from holders of six series of its debt securities for the planned spin-off of its U.K.-based Gallaher tobacco business.</p>
<p>American Brands said it expects to spin off the business on May 30, 1997.</p>
<p>((New York Newsdesk 212 859 1610))</p>
